title: Best match I've played to date! Really feel like getting to Gold this season will be possible!

embed.description: Imgur: The most awesome images on the Internet.

body: Just proud of how well I did in this promo match! I feel like I will be able to get Gold if I keep this up! Really proud of my ranked journey so far this year. Started at Bronze 5 and Now I'm Silver 3!  Now to work on to Silver 2!
